WEBVTT

00:00:00.733 --> 00:00:04.895
mit ayer erloybenish foroys, mit kasete numer tsvey.

00:00:05.711 --> 00:00:07.612
ir hot oyfgehert

00:00:08.242 --> 00:00:14.070
tsu dertseyln vi mir zenen geven bay dem goy vos hot aykh ge- badarft firn keyn geto SHAVLI.

00:00:14.098 --> 00:00:14.970
bite,

00:00:15.245 --> 00:00:16.319
dertseyln SIE.

00:00:15.414 --> 00:00:17.653
ya, zaynen mir gekumen mit dem

00:00:18.148 --> 00:00:20.870
mit dem mentshn, mit dem poyer fun dorf

00:00:20.898 --> 00:00:23.469
le- mit di fur zayne, lebn Tel-

00:00:23.469 --> 00:00:24.549
in, in geto

00:00:24.549 --> 00:00:26.563
in TELŠIAI, lebn toyer,

00:00:26.788 --> 00:00:29.584
un in der tsayt flegt er nemen oyf der arbet

00:00:29.690 --> 00:00:33.155
yung- meydlekh tsu der arbet, oyf farshidene land-arbet.

00:00:33.200 --> 00:00:34.900
hot er gezogt er nemt undz

00:00:34.900 --> 00:00:37.262
a- tsu der arbet grobn bulves.

00:00:38.567 --> 00:00:44.080
vos hobn mir gehat in geto? mir hobn gehat a kishn mit a deke vos mir hobn gekrogn fun komitet,

00:00:44.439 --> 00:00:47.049
mit ⟨aza⟩ kleydl, mit a mantl.

00:00:47.173 --> 00:00:49.496
hobn mir dos genumen undzere zakhn

00:00:49.569 --> 00:00:50.697
un mir zayn-

00:00:50.717 --> 00:00:52.216
mit im avekgeforn

00:00:52.235 --> 00:00:53.394
tsu im aheym.

00:00:53.990 --> 00:00:57.376
di veg hot oykh zeyer geregnt, geven aza shlekhter veg.

00:00:57.888 --> 00:01:01.291
nu, m'iz geforn, m'iz gekumen bay im in shtub.

00:01:02.023 --> 00:01:04.228
firt undz arayn in shtub,

00:01:04.941 --> 00:01:08.109
gefunen a froy mit dray kleyne kinderlekh,

00:01:09.060 --> 00:01:10.472
gants azoy

00:01:10.578 --> 00:01:12.564
basheydn gelebt

00:01:13.127 --> 00:01:16.041
ober zeyer fayne mentshn, gute,

00:01:16.637 --> 00:01:18.994
glaykh gegebn undz esn.

00:01:19.472 --> 00:01:21.139
m'hot undz ongeton

00:01:21.139 --> 00:01:22.385
varemer

00:01:22.880 --> 00:01:25.861
un di nakht zaynen mir durkhgeshlofn bay zey.

00:01:25.985 --> 00:01:28.072
dos iz geven in detsember monat.

00:01:28.989 --> 00:01:30.705
detsember velkhe yor?

00:01:30.677 --> 00:01:32.123
eyn un fertsik.

00:01:33.630 --> 00:01:35.362
oyf baginen

00:01:36.617 --> 00:01:39.837
hot er ayngeshpart dem f- ayngeshpant dem ferd

00:01:39.837 --> 00:01:41.201
in a shlitn,

00:01:42.219 --> 00:01:44.626
un s'iz nokh gezesn nokh a litvishe froy,

00:01:44.733 --> 00:01:48.575
ober zi hot nit gevust keyn zakh. mir hobn mi- mit keynem nit geredt

00:01:49.509 --> 00:01:54.105
un zi hot undz nokh di froy ongeton mit hentshkes vareme gedenk ikh,

00:01:54.133 --> 00:01:56.248
mit tikhlekh,

00:01:56.293 --> 00:01:58.813
un gegebn a labn dorfishe broyt,

00:01:58.841 --> 00:02:01.285
far yedern gemakht azane pekelekh

00:02:01.285 --> 00:02:03.037
vi azoy vi me geyt fun dorf

00:02:04.916 --> 00:02:07.006
un arayngezetst zikh in shlitn

00:02:07.006 --> 00:02:08.302
un mir zaynen geforn

00:02:08.678 --> 00:02:10.191
kimat di gantse nakht.

00:02:13.556 --> 00:02:15.896
baginen zaynen mir gekumen in Shavl.

00:02:16.830 --> 00:02:18.613
Shavl iz a groyse shtot.

00:02:19.243 --> 00:02:21.515
mir zaynen gekumen bay eyn breg shtot.

00:02:23.563 --> 00:02:26.817
dortn, der rayon hot zikh ongerufn, in GUBERNIJA.

00:02:26.817 --> 00:02:28.985
GUBERNIJA iz geven in Shavl a groyser

00:02:29.013 --> 00:02:30.189
bir-f-

00:02:31.106 --> 00:02:33.750
bir-fabrik vu m'hot oysgearbet bir.

00:02:33.958 --> 00:02:37.479
dos iz eyn breg shtot fun di same tsentrale gas.

00:02:38.767 --> 00:02:40.871
un mir hobn gedarft avekgeyn

00:02:40.961 --> 00:02:42.840
in di tsveyte breg shtot.

00:02:42.840 --> 00:02:44.938
s'iz geven a groyser leder-fabrik

00:02:45.956 --> 00:02:48.549
vu dortn hobn gearbet s- yidn fun geto.

00:02:49.179 --> 00:02:51.317
m'hot gedarft durkhgeyn di gantse shtot.

00:02:52.503 --> 00:02:54.407
iz er mit undz gegangen.

00:02:54.410 --> 00:02:57.020
er hot getrogn undzere beyde pekelekh

00:02:57.279 --> 00:02:59.298
un mir zaynen gegangen hinter im

00:03:01.363 --> 00:03:03.613
un mir zaynen durkh di gantse shtot

00:03:03.658 --> 00:03:06.217
un gekumen dortn oyfn fabrik.

00:03:06.611 --> 00:03:10.487
demolts gegangen ⟨hot,⟩ zent ir mit di lates oder on di...? on di lates.

00:03:09.007 --> 00:03:11.818
neyn, on di lates. mir zaynen gegangen on di late-

00:03:10.627 --> 00:03:12.360
un keyner hot aykh nisht getshepet?

00:03:11.818 --> 00:03:14.708
keyner hot nit getshepet. keyner hot nit gekukt oyf undz.

00:03:16.618 --> 00:03:19.684
zaynen mir gekumen oyf, in leder-fabrik

00:03:20.381 --> 00:03:23.618
un dortn hobn mir zikh shoyn arayngemisht tsvishn di arbeter,

00:03:23.618 --> 00:03:24.864
tsvishn alemen,

00:03:25.241 --> 00:03:28.290
un az di mentshn zaynen shoyn gegangen fun fabrik aheym

00:03:29.004 --> 00:03:31.532
zaynen mir arayn mit zey tsuzamen in geto.

00:03:31.532 --> 00:03:34.376
baym toyer hot men nit kontrolirt ver es kumt arayn.

00:03:34.376 --> 00:03:35.647
meyle, m'iz arayn.

00:03:36.716 --> 00:03:38.837
un der litviner, er iz avek

00:03:39.213 --> 00:03:40.844
tsurik bay zikh aheym.

00:03:41.897 --> 00:03:43.427
avekgeforn aheym.

00:03:43.263 --> 00:03:46.239
heyst dos ongekumen zent ir keyn geto Shavl

00:03:46.239 --> 00:03:47.730
DEKABR'

00:03:47.145 --> 00:03:50.025
eyn un fertsik. nayntsn eyn un fertsik.

00:03:50.098 --> 00:03:56.600
hob ikh nor gevolt a kurtse frage fregn. di frierike geto, vi hot ir gerufn dem plats? vu hot geven di frierike geto?

00:03:55.751 --> 00:03:56.859
TELŠIAI.

00:03:56.600 --> 00:03:57.904
TELŠIAI.

00:03:57.033 --> 00:03:58.681
Telzh oyf yidish, Telzh.

00:03:57.904 --> 00:04:01.654
zayendik in TELŠIAI, vifl zent ir geven dortn in geto in TELŠIAI?

00:04:01.033 --> 00:04:03.508
nu, a tsvey monat nit, nit mer.

00:04:02.298 --> 00:04:03.524
tsvey monat.

00:04:03.868 --> 00:04:04.926
tsvey dray.

00:04:03.969 --> 00:04:08.958
dort iz geven a yidisher komitet organizirt. s'iz geven dort oykh yidishe politsey?

00:04:06.348 --> 00:04:07.203
ye.

00:04:08.627 --> 00:04:10.410
neyn, keyn zakh iz nit geven.

00:04:10.230 --> 00:04:11.524
bloyz a komitet.

00:04:10.410 --> 00:04:12.688
key-, bloyz a komitet. keyne-

00:04:11.799 --> 00:04:14.595
vi flegn, vi hobn zikh oyfgefirt di, di yidishe...

00:04:13.638 --> 00:04:17.261
neyn, gut, fayn, zeyer fayn. s'iz geven reyne froyen.

00:04:15.596 --> 00:04:18.712
zey hobn mitgehol- m'hot gehol- mitgeholfn di mentshn?

00:04:18.363 --> 00:04:21.884
ye, ye. m'hot geholfn. m'hot dortn gekokht a k- esn.

00:04:21.958 --> 00:04:24.925
dortn dakht zikh, ya. m'hot gekokht. m'hot gegebn esn.

00:04:24.925 --> 00:04:26.829
m'hot gegebn a bisl zakhn.

00:04:25.788 --> 00:04:27.639
a, s'iz geven a tsentrale kikh?

00:04:27.476 --> 00:04:30.407
s'iz geven mis- ⟨s'iz mis-⟩, geven a kikh epes. ya.

00:04:30.716 --> 00:04:32.769
gedenk shoyn azoy nit altsding genoy.

00:04:34.867 --> 00:04:36.771
bite, dertseyln SIE vayter vegn

00:04:36.771 --> 00:04:37.730
SHAVLI.

00:04:37.365 --> 00:04:41.173
SHAVLI, zaynen mir arayn in, mit di brigade in geto.

00:04:41.921 --> 00:04:46.016
mir hobn zikh dervust vu di kh-, nokhgefregt vu di mishpokhe lebt,

00:04:46.292 --> 00:04:48.227
grade nit vayt fun toyer.

00:04:49.228 --> 00:04:51.281
nu, un mir zaynen avek tsu zey.

00:04:51.489 --> 00:04:54.302
mir zaynen geven mit zey bakant fun forn krig.

00:04:55.421 --> 00:04:58.042
zeyer a sheyne mishpokhe, a fayne,

00:04:58.042 --> 00:04:59.921
hot undz zeyer fayn oyfgenumen.

00:05:00.129 --> 00:05:02.835
im hot men gerufn, dem balebos,

00:05:02.835 --> 00:05:04.680
Heshl Uryashevitsh.

00:05:05.597 --> 00:05:08.545
iz, di froy iz geven Mashe Uryashevitsh.

00:05:08.769 --> 00:05:11.598
geven a tokhter Rayele Uryashevitsh.

00:05:12.633 --> 00:05:16.256
zi hot nokh gelebt in, nokh zikh bafrayt fun di lagern,

00:05:16.599 --> 00:05:21.504
gelebt in Yisroel, ober ikh, az ikh bin gekumen hob ikh ir shoyn nit getrofn, iz zi geshtorbn.

00:05:21.932 --> 00:05:24.508
un a bruderl iz geven bay zey, YITSKHAK.

00:05:25.728 --> 00:05:27.849
er iz oykh umgekumen in di lagern

00:05:27.939 --> 00:05:29.030
mit di mamen.

00:05:31.415 --> 00:05:34.177
nu, arayn in geto, gelebt bay zey.

00:05:34.706 --> 00:05:38.227
zey hobn undz gehaltn zeyer gut, punkt vi eygene kinder.

00:05:39.347 --> 00:05:41.856
fun onfang zaynen mir nokh nit gegangen arbetn.

00:05:43.970 --> 00:05:46.969
s'iz geven shver in geto, mitn esn.

00:05:47.193 --> 00:05:48.419
m'hot gehungert.

00:05:50.214 --> 00:05:52.540
un nakher in a kurtse tsayt arum ⟨nit⟩,

00:05:52.540 --> 00:05:56.604
in a halb yor arum umgefer, zaynen mir oykh gegangen ar- ongefangen geyn arbetn.

00:05:57.352 --> 00:05:59.169
⟨ge- arbetn⟩ oyfn erodrom.

00:05:59.276 --> 00:06:02.561
m'hot gefirt g- zeyer a sakh mentshn fun geto.

00:06:01.588 --> 00:06:03.894
bay vos hot ir gearbet perzenlekh?

00:06:02.786 --> 00:06:05.767
bayn, bayn grobn transheyen epes.

00:06:06.296 --> 00:06:07.837
khotsh s'iz geven vinter

00:06:07.848 --> 00:06:09.749
un gehakt mit di kirkes,

00:06:10.700 --> 00:06:13.006
un der daytsh iz, do iz shoyn geven daytshn.

00:06:14.970 --> 00:06:19.194
nu, in geto farshteyt zikh iz bay toyer zaynen oykh geshtanen litvishe politsey.

00:06:19.194 --> 00:06:21.073
s'iz geven yidishe politsey.

00:06:22.378 --> 00:06:26.743
ober azoy vi mir zaynen nor geven yunge meydlekh, mir hobn zikh in ergets nit gemisht.

00:06:29.162 --> 00:06:32.464
m'iz gegangen arbetn bay, in erodrom a lange tsayt.

00:06:32.975 --> 00:06:36.547
nakher hot men undz aribergefirt arbetn bay daytshn

00:06:37.329 --> 00:06:38.825
bay di WEHRMACHT.

00:06:38.898 --> 00:06:39.466
d-

00:06:39.573 --> 00:06:41.660
nu, dortn iz shoyn geven ne-, zaynen zey geven

00:06:41.784 --> 00:06:42.380
iz ge-

00:06:42.380 --> 00:06:45.373
a bisl epes mentshisher, nit azane khayes.

00:06:45.463 --> 00:06:48.208
vos far a arbet iz geven bay di WEHRMACHT?

00:06:48.129 --> 00:06:54.688
m'hot geramt bay zey, m'hot gekert, m'hot ge- geholfn dortn, ale, ale shvartse arbet tsu ton.

00:06:55.166 --> 00:06:58.015
di mener hobn gehakt holts, ge⟨UNK⟩ dem hoyf,

00:06:58.015 --> 00:06:59.703
un mir froyen hobn geramt di sh-

00:06:59.703 --> 00:07:01.489
di dire, di sh- tsimern.

00:07:01.848 --> 00:07:04.070
un dos iz shoyn geven onfang

00:07:04.464 --> 00:07:05.347
⟨tsu⟩ in tsvey

00:07:04.565 --> 00:07:05.471
nayntsn...

00:07:05.347 --> 00:07:07.529
tsvey un fertsik, shoyn in geto.

00:07:06.354 --> 00:07:10.533
un ir hot nokh biz demolst nisht gevust vos iz geshen mit ayere familye.

00:07:09.560 --> 00:07:15.022
mir hobn, mir hobn gevust a- neyn, keyn zakh nit gevust vos s'iz geshen. neyn, neyn, keyn zakh nit.

00:07:12.699 --> 00:07:14.347
demolst hot ir nokh nisht gevust.

00:07:15.247 --> 00:07:18.552
m'hot gevust az m'hot oysgeharget umetum di yidn in di shtetlekh.

00:07:18.318 --> 00:07:20.675
ober spetsyel vos hot mit zey geshen?

00:07:18.552 --> 00:07:21.249
ober azoy spetsyel keyn zakh nit.

00:07:24.157 --> 00:07:30.137
nu, nakher arib-, dort, bay di daytshn gearbet. nakher hobn mi- hot men undz aribergefirt arbetn

00:07:30.137 --> 00:07:32.558
nokh in, bay andere daytshn,

00:07:32.558 --> 00:07:33.770
in groyse

00:07:34.147 --> 00:07:36.946
nu, skladn dortn fun produktn

00:07:36.946 --> 00:07:39.013
vos flegt geyn fa- oyfn front, far di

00:07:39.013 --> 00:07:41.938
konservn, kompotn, alts azane zakhn.

00:07:42.045 --> 00:07:46.832
mir oykh dort, se hot shoyn get- -arbet oykh nit untern dakh, nit oyf droysn.

00:07:49.875 --> 00:07:51.270
nu, in Shavl,

00:07:51.377 --> 00:07:53.413
in Shavl iz geven tsvey getos.

00:07:54.465 --> 00:07:57.058
eyne hot zikh gerufn Traker geto

00:07:57.148 --> 00:07:59.454
s'iz oyf yidish, un oyf litvish TRAKŲ.

00:08:00.101 --> 00:08:03.015
di tsveyte geto iz geven Kavkazer geto.

00:08:03.273 --> 00:08:05.225
KAUKAZAS oyf litvish.

00:08:05.450 --> 00:08:07.351
far vos tsvey getos?

00:08:08.167 --> 00:08:10.358
vayle s'iz nit geven keyn

00:08:10.361 --> 00:08:14.248
ort far alemen, a groyser shetekh aza, me zol alemen in eyn ort.

00:08:14.276 --> 00:08:16.256
hot men dos gemakht in tsvey erter.

00:08:16.256 --> 00:08:18.320
ober keyn untersheyd iz nit geven.

00:08:18.478 --> 00:08:21.977
fun di mentshn, fun, un fun der gantser stroy, fun altsding.

00:08:21.977 --> 00:08:23.534
di zelbe zakh umetum.

00:08:27.742 --> 00:08:28.254
mm

00:08:28.254 --> 00:08:29.508
un in

00:08:30.594 --> 00:08:34.574
nayntsn dray un fertsik iz geven in Shavler geto

00:08:34.577 --> 00:08:36.090
a kinder-aktsye.

00:08:37.647 --> 00:08:39.396
vos heyst a kinder-aktsye?

00:08:38.777 --> 00:08:41.862
m'hot tsugenumen, arayngekumen di daytshn,

00:08:41.882 --> 00:08:43.901
litviner, ukrainer,

00:08:44.330 --> 00:08:49.218
un m'hot, un oyf ale mentshn zaynen avek dem tog tsu der arbet, arbets-feike.

00:08:49.443 --> 00:08:52.391
geblibn alte, kranke mit kinder

00:08:52.869 --> 00:08:54.669
un m'hot alemen tsugenumen.

00:08:55.772 --> 00:08:57.302
m'hot aroysgefirt

00:08:58.742 --> 00:09:02.230
un m'hot zey ⟨alemen⟩ in Daytshland, zogt men, aroysgefirt zey,

00:09:02.319 --> 00:09:03.928
un m'hot alemen farnikhtet.

00:09:03.928 --> 00:09:05.992
dos hot zikh ongerufn di kinder-aktsye.

00:09:07.938 --> 00:09:09.957
gekumen fun der arbet ale

00:09:10.183 --> 00:09:13.344
un m'hot nit gefunen keyn kinder, keynem nit, di yeloles,

00:09:13.355 --> 00:09:17.484
di veynerayen vos s'iz geven shreklekh dan vos s'hot geton dem tog in geto.

00:09:19.650 --> 00:09:26.327
vi hobn zikh mentshn, di eltere mentshn, gegebn a eytse in geto mit esn, m- vi si-

00:09:25.775 --> 00:09:28.523
in geto iz ge- ershtns in geto iz geven a gesheft

00:09:28.523 --> 00:09:30.090
un s'iz geven kartetshkes.

00:09:30.720 --> 00:09:31.822
m'hot gegebn

00:09:31.822 --> 00:09:33.617
epes vos a bisele.

00:09:34.213 --> 00:09:37.467
nu, un dan mentshn zaynen aro- flegn geyn tsu der arbet in shtot.

00:09:37.467 --> 00:09:39.911
mentshn zaynen arayn mit zakhn in geto,

00:09:40.187 --> 00:09:42.949
di hige mentshn, fun shtot, fun Shavl.

00:09:43.275 --> 00:09:45.159
flegt men aroysgeyn tsu der arbet. f-

00:09:45.249 --> 00:09:47.254
flegn kumen poyerim

00:09:47.291 --> 00:09:49.060
oyf di arbets-pletser

00:09:49.060 --> 00:09:50.756
un me flegt oysbaytn.

00:09:50.801 --> 00:09:55.065
far kh- zakh flegt men gebn a shtikl broyt, a shtikl puter.

00:09:55.222 --> 00:09:57.410
m'hot zikh gedreyt vi nit iz.

00:09:58.513 --> 00:09:59.469
un

00:09:59.778 --> 00:10:05.999
in di dires hot men gelebt zeyer eng. in tsimer hobn gelebt tsu dray fir mishpokhes

00:10:06.748 --> 00:10:08.568
umgefer. mir hobn gelebt

00:10:08.587 --> 00:10:10.711
bay, mit di mishpokhe Uryashevitsh,

00:10:10.711 --> 00:10:12.480
hobn mir gelebt in a kikh.

00:10:13.278 --> 00:10:16.259
zaynen zey geven fir, un mir tsvey, zeks mentshn.

00:10:16.856 --> 00:10:18.684
un dortn flegt men kokhn

00:10:18.684 --> 00:10:20.152
ale shkhey- un s'iz geven

00:10:20.152 --> 00:10:23.195
nokh tsvey tsimern, hobn gelebt nokh mishpokhes.

00:10:23.420 --> 00:10:24.101
nu?

00:10:24.112 --> 00:10:25.896
UNK un ale hobn zikh gedreyt.

00:10:26.795 --> 00:10:29.205
s'iz geven

00:10:29.242 --> 00:10:35.733
⟨EYZE⟩ spetsyele krankeytn in in tsayt fun geto vos ir gedenkt? s'iz geven faln fun epidemyes un un?

00:10:35.300 --> 00:10:38.327
nu, dos vey- kh'veys nit ⟨ikh⟩ veys dos nit.

00:10:36.127 --> 00:10:37.353
gedenkt ir nisht?

00:10:38.338 --> 00:10:40.816
nu, ikh shtel zikh for az s'iz ye geven mistomen

00:10:40.785 --> 00:10:42.011
yetst az ir...

00:10:40.835 --> 00:10:42.129
fun aza lebn.

00:10:42.320 --> 00:10:48.626
az mir redn ve- vegn, dortn iz geven zogt ir in Shavl iz yo geven a yidisher komitet un yidishe politsey.

00:10:48.243 --> 00:10:48.997
ye.

00:10:49.020 --> 00:10:51.009
vi flegn zey zikh oyffirn

00:10:51.009 --> 00:10:52.316
loyt ayer meynung,

00:10:52.316 --> 00:10:53.401
yene tsaytn?

00:10:53.694 --> 00:10:57.975
nu, in Shavl di politsey geven nit a- nit keyn shlekhte, meyn ikh azoy.

00:10:58.115 --> 00:11:01.788
s'iz, nu, s'iz geven farsh- efsher eyntslne faln vos geven.

00:11:01.457 --> 00:11:03.274
ober ir perzenlekh hot shoyn...

00:11:01.845 --> 00:11:06.024
o- ikh perzenlekh, ikh perzenlekh, mir, mir hobn nit keyn zakh nit geshpirt.

00:11:06.536 --> 00:11:11.824
der komitet, nu, gem- gefirt zeyer program vos zey hobn gedarft. s'iz geven a am-

00:11:11.824 --> 00:11:14.186
vegn arbets-amt vos se flegt firn,

00:11:14.214 --> 00:11:16.402
shikn oyf der arbet mentshn.

00:11:16.661 --> 00:11:19.794
o- ir perzenlekh hot ir nisht gehat keyn shum problemen mit zey?

00:11:18.939 --> 00:11:20.317
neyn, neyn.

00:11:21.032 --> 00:11:23.710
keyne problemen nit gehat mitn komitet.

00:11:23.850 --> 00:11:29.281
ir hot gevust, s'iz geven epes faln az s'iz geven a untererd-arbet in geto?

00:11:29.317 --> 00:11:35.336
s'iz geven epes mentshn vos flegn opgehat farbindungen mit partizaner, ep- oyb ir veyst epes vegn dem?

00:11:34.464 --> 00:11:36.467
ikh perzenlekh veys dos nit.

00:11:36.067 --> 00:11:37.262
ir veyst nisht vegn dem.

00:11:36.523 --> 00:11:37.840
neyn. neyn, ney-

00:11:37.262 --> 00:11:38.964
ir hot de- demolst nokh nisht gevu-

00:11:38.092 --> 00:11:40.989
ikh hob nit keyn zakh nit gevust, neyn, neyn.

00:11:39.206 --> 00:11:40.753
nisht gevust vegn dem.

00:11:41.703 --> 00:11:42.541
un

00:11:42.750 --> 00:11:45.793
eyn tsayt hot men undz aroysgefirt zumer. dos iz geven

00:11:45.793 --> 00:11:48.398
mistome in dray un fertsikstn yor meyn ikh,

00:11:49.078 --> 00:11:49.933
oyf

00:11:50.107 --> 00:11:52.160
arbet bay torf,

00:11:53.398 --> 00:11:54.911
hinter Shavl.

00:11:55.406 --> 00:11:57.037
geven tsvey lagern.

00:11:57.498 --> 00:11:59.838
eyner hot zikh gerufn BUČIŪNAI,

00:12:00.671 --> 00:12:02.403
geven a groyser lager.

00:12:03.033 --> 00:12:05.798
un der tsveyter iz geven KARPIŠKIAI.

00:12:05.798 --> 00:12:07.770
s- alts litvishe nemen.

00:12:08.062 --> 00:12:10.065
mir zaynen geven in KARPIŠKIAI.

00:12:11.842 --> 00:12:14.199
dortn oykh nor litviner politsey.

00:12:14.340 --> 00:12:16.258
daytshn zaynen dort nit geven.

00:12:16.753 --> 00:12:17.535
ober

00:12:17.535 --> 00:12:19.667
farheltenishmesik iz nokh geven

00:12:19.959 --> 00:12:21.320
nit shlekht azoy.

00:12:21.900 --> 00:12:25.725
flegn aroyslozn in dorf, un flegt zikh kenen bazorgn esn.

00:12:25.848 --> 00:12:28.829
nu, di arbet iz geven shvere, nit laykht.

00:12:29.510 --> 00:12:31.990
az m'iz geven iber a khoydesh dortn zumer.

00:12:31.990 --> 00:12:34.150
nakher hot men undz tsurikgebrakht in geto.

00:12:36.092 --> 00:12:40.291
nakher iz nokh geven, f- hot men gefirt oyf di arbet bay kalkh-arbet.

00:12:40.291 --> 00:12:41.368
AKMENĖ.

00:12:43.719 --> 00:12:48.911
dort- dortn bin ikh nit geven, nor mayn kuzine iz dortn geven oyf der ar- in, dort in dem, AKMENĖ.

00:12:48.815 --> 00:12:52.842
ayer kuzine iz geven di zelbe elter vi ir, O zi iz geven elter fun aykh?

00:12:52.157 --> 00:12:54.311
z- onderhalbn yor elter fun mir.

00:13:01.387 --> 00:13:03.322
UNK dortn.

00:13:04.695 --> 00:13:08.942
nakher hot men undz, nakh- nakher zaynen mir shoyn geven nor in Shavler geto.

00:13:08.998 --> 00:13:12.249
un in fir un fertsikstn yor hot men genumen shoyn

00:13:12.896 --> 00:13:16.434
aroysfirn fun geto in Daytshland, in di lagern.

00:13:17.857 --> 00:13:18.512
mayn

00:13:18.512 --> 00:13:21.227
mayn ku- mir hobn zikh tsesheydt mit di kuzine.

00:13:21.502 --> 00:13:25.769
zi iz geven in AKMENer lager. zi hot gehat shoyn a man in geto,

00:13:25.769 --> 00:13:27.169
geven khasene gehat.

00:13:27.169 --> 00:13:29.495
hot men zey aroysgefirt in Daytshland.

00:13:31.290 --> 00:13:33.816
un ikh bin geblibn in Shavler geto.

00:13:35.593 --> 00:13:36.431
un a

00:13:36.487 --> 00:13:39.991
shoyn farn likvidirn di geto a kurtse tsayt,

00:13:40.115 --> 00:13:42.551
a monat farn likvidirn di geto,

00:13:42.551 --> 00:13:44.547
hot zikh mir gemakht a fal,

00:13:46.207 --> 00:13:47.484
az

00:13:47.979 --> 00:13:50.049
ikh bin aroys fun geto

00:13:50.831 --> 00:13:54.521
oykh durkh bakantshaft. dur-, bakante mentshn hobn mir geholfn.

00:13:55.151 --> 00:13:57.407
bin aroys durkhn t- durkhn tsam,

00:13:57.817 --> 00:14:00.039
gemakht a lokh in di shtakhl-drot,

00:14:00.703 --> 00:14:03.853
un durkhn tsam, un ikh hob gehat a adres in shtot

00:14:04.871 --> 00:14:06.874
vu tsu geyn, bay litviner.

00:14:06.845 --> 00:14:08.679
ver hot aykh gegebn dem adres?

00:14:07.959 --> 00:14:10.653
oykh a ba- eyner a bakanter fun geto.

00:14:11.351 --> 00:14:13.185
un ikh bin dortn avek.

00:14:13.393 --> 00:14:15.396
dem baginen bay tsu zey.

00:14:16.211 --> 00:14:18.011
gekumen tsu zey,

00:14:18.978 --> 00:14:20.677
mir arayngelozn,

00:14:22.218 --> 00:14:25.098
un ikh hob shoyn dortn bay zey gefunen mentshn yidn.

00:14:26.420 --> 00:14:29.064
ikh gedenk nit di familye d- fun di mentshn.

00:14:30.453 --> 00:14:33.350
un fun dortn flegn zey avekfirn oyfn dorf.

00:14:38.469 --> 00:14:40.809
mir oykh nakher avekgefirt

00:14:41.490 --> 00:14:42.986
in PAGELAVA,

00:14:43.700 --> 00:14:44.741
in a dorf.

00:14:47.666 --> 00:14:50.987
un fun PAGELAVA hot men nokh avekgefirt durkh a vald

00:14:50.990 --> 00:14:52.582
bay an ander mentshn.

00:14:52.582 --> 00:14:53.364
bay a

00:14:54.180 --> 00:14:55.004
dorf,

00:14:55.004 --> 00:14:56.047
dorf-mentsh.

00:14:56.407 --> 00:15:00.215
hobn gelebt eyne aleyn in a groyse shtub dortn a mishpokhe,

00:15:00.710 --> 00:15:03.489
un dortn bay zey bin ikh geven a monat tsayt

00:15:04.507 --> 00:15:06.408
biz m'hot bafrayt Shavl.

00:15:08.304 --> 00:15:12.483
az ir hot zikh antlofn fun geto kedey zikh oystsubahaltn

00:15:12.843 --> 00:15:17.930
hot ir shoyn gehat a anung vegn dem, az di sovyetishe armey geyt foroys un v-

00:15:17.930 --> 00:15:21.174
s'vet bald in kurtsn zayn bafrayt? ir hot gehat epes a anung vegn dem?

00:15:20.890 --> 00:15:25.193
m'hot a bisl ya geredt in geto. m'hot shoyn geredt a bisl. s'iz geven yedies.

00:15:25.193 --> 00:15:26.374
mentshn hobn in sh-

00:15:26.374 --> 00:15:27.606
zey likvidirn shoyn.

00:15:27.606 --> 00:15:30.540
s'kumt shoyn der sof. me likvidirt shoyn di getos...

00:15:30.107 --> 00:15:32.008
m'hot shoyn gehat a anung vegn dem.

00:15:31.170 --> 00:15:33.966
anung, m'hot shoyn farshtanen epes vos, ya.

00:15:37.110 --> 00:15:42.741
nor m'hot bafrayt Sh- ikh bin geven dortn bay zey a monat tsayt. nakher hot men bafrayt Shavl.

00:15:42.577 --> 00:15:44.073
ven iz dos geven?

00:15:44.872 --> 00:15:48.005
ven hot men bafrayt Shavl? in fir un fertsikstn yor.

00:15:48.146 --> 00:15:49.878
zumer fir un fertsik?

00:15:49.277 --> 00:15:50.081
ye.

00:15:52.010 --> 00:15:55.500
iz, zaynen mir avekgef- bin ikh avekgeforn dan fun zey

00:15:55.503 --> 00:15:56.797
in Shavl

00:15:57.225 --> 00:15:59.008
nokh di bafrayung.

00:15:59.790 --> 00:16:03.514
nu, m'hot shoyn genumen klaybn a bisl yidn fun umetum

00:16:04.160 --> 00:16:06.385
fun Daytshland iz nokh keyner nit gekumen.

00:16:06.385 --> 00:16:09.740
nor fun Lite, ver es iz ⟨zikh⟩ shoyn vu, epes vu bafrayt

00:16:11.720 --> 00:16:14.131
zaynen mir geven a kurtse tsayt in Shavl

00:16:14.131 --> 00:16:17.081
un der daytsh hot dan nokh a mol ongegrifn Shavl,

00:16:17.323 --> 00:16:19.522
hot di hige makht fun shtot

00:16:19.522 --> 00:16:22.549
geheysn ale yidn avekforn vos gikher fun Shavl.

00:16:22.672 --> 00:16:24.776
mir zoln nit araynfaln a tsveytn mol.

00:16:26.250 --> 00:16:27.442
gedenk ikh vi haynt.

00:16:27.347 --> 00:16:29.070
un ir f- ir hot take avekgefor-

00:16:28.275 --> 00:16:30.829
ya, avekgeforn ⟨o-⟩ in frakht-vagones,

00:16:30.829 --> 00:16:33.157
oyf shteyner zaynen mir dan geforn.

00:16:33.202 --> 00:16:35.053
mir zaynen avekgeforn in Kovne.

00:16:36.189 --> 00:16:40.689
un dan zaynen mir avek fun Shavl shoyn. mer ⟨hob ikh⟩ zikh shoyn nit umgekert in Shavl,

00:16:40.847 --> 00:16:42.748
un zikh opgeshtelt in Kovne.

00:16:45.690 --> 00:16:46.539
mm

00:16:46.539 --> 00:16:48.952
gekumen dan in Kovne,

00:16:48.963 --> 00:16:52.231
gey ikh in aza shtub, hobn zikh genumen ale klaybn

00:16:53.368 --> 00:16:54.124
un in

00:16:54.127 --> 00:16:58.981
iber hoypt iz men gegangen in Kovne iz do a groyse shul, a khor-sh-, di khor-shul.

00:16:59.426 --> 00:17:02.073
oyf OŽEŠKIENĖS ruft zikh on di gas.

00:17:02.109 --> 00:17:05.321
dortn flegt men undz, hobn zikh genumen klaybn oykh a sakh.

00:17:05.321 --> 00:17:07.582
m'hot zikh farregistrirt dortn.

00:17:07.627 --> 00:17:10.873
vayle mentshn flegn kumen zukhn, efsher iz ver lebn geblibn.

00:17:10.873 --> 00:17:12.566
fraynd, eygene.

00:17:14.377 --> 00:17:16.754
ikh hob zikh oykh dan dortn farshribn.

00:17:16.790 --> 00:17:19.164
nor gefunen in YAD VASHEM di

00:17:20.148 --> 00:17:21.572
di SPIS- di

00:17:21.465 --> 00:17:22.202
list.

00:17:22.053 --> 00:17:23.208
di listes

00:17:23.220 --> 00:17:24.716
fun di farshribene.

00:17:27.135 --> 00:17:30.336
nu, zikh ongefangen a n- vider a nayer lebn.

00:17:31.843 --> 00:17:33.592
nu, m'iz geven yung.

00:17:34.678 --> 00:17:36.008
ikh bin gekumen,

00:17:36.028 --> 00:17:37.794
keynem nit gefunen.

00:17:39.791 --> 00:17:41.602
in a kurtse tsayt arum

00:17:41.602 --> 00:17:44.139
bin ikh avekgeforn bay undz in shtetl.

00:17:44.516 --> 00:17:48.847
dan hob ikh zikh dervust fun di gantse tragedye vos dortn iz forgekumen.

00:17:48.144 --> 00:17:50.940
fun vemen hot ir zikh dervust? ver hot aykh dertseylt?

00:17:50.034 --> 00:17:53.791
fun li- fun litviner. ven ikh, kh'hob gefunen undzer gevezene

00:17:54.000 --> 00:17:55.581
shtub-arbeterin

00:17:56.244 --> 00:17:57.453
KAROLINA.

00:17:56.390 --> 00:17:58.567
v- vos hot zi aykh dertseylt?

00:17:58.083 --> 00:18:01.827
nu, hot zi dertseylt vi zi f- ⟨vu m'hot⟩ tsuzamengetribn dan

00:18:01.827 --> 00:18:03.984
bay undz in mitn shtetl iz geven aza

00:18:04.074 --> 00:18:07.290
gortn, aza plats, skver vi me ruft dos.

00:18:07.550 --> 00:18:10.312
dort hot men tsuzamengetribn alemen,

00:18:10.740 --> 00:18:13.147
m'hot gepaynikt, m'hot geharget.

00:18:13.322 --> 00:18:17.755
zi fleg kumen tsu zey. zi flegt zey brengen esn, di mamen, dem bruder.

00:18:18.047 --> 00:18:20.505
flegt lozn, nit lozn, vi a mol.

00:18:21.370 --> 00:18:25.258
nu, nakher hot zi dertseylt vi m'hot zey oysgeshosn ⟨un zey⟩ avekgeharget.

00:18:25.269 --> 00:18:27.705
dos oykh nit vayt fun Kretinge.

00:18:27.750 --> 00:18:30.444
lebn Kretinge iz do a kurort, PALANGA,

00:18:30.720 --> 00:18:32.978
tsvelf kilometer fun Kretinge.

00:18:32.978 --> 00:18:35.945
iz unter vegs fun Kretinge, PALANGA,

00:18:36.002 --> 00:18:37.231
in a veldl

00:18:37.231 --> 00:18:38.881
shteyt a denkmol

00:18:39.191 --> 00:18:41.345
az dortn hot men avekgeharget...

00:18:40.423 --> 00:18:42.527
ver hot oyfgeshtelt dem denkmol?

00:18:42.532 --> 00:18:44.062
di melukhe f-, dakht zikh.

00:18:44.456 --> 00:18:48.014
ober s'iz nit ongeshribn az s'iz yidn oder vos, keyn zakh nit.

00:18:47.190 --> 00:18:48.129
birger.

00:18:48.014 --> 00:18:48.956
birger.

00:18:49.485 --> 00:18:52.702
vos hot ir dervust, vos hot ir zikh dervust vegn tatn?

00:18:49.535 --> 00:18:50.728
oyf litvish.

00:18:52.252 --> 00:18:57.388
nu, vegn foter hob ikh zikh dervust az, dem baginen az s'hot ongefangen di milkhome

00:18:57.388 --> 00:18:59.014
iz er geven in dorf.

00:18:59.205 --> 00:19:01.562
dos iz zibn kilometer fun Kretinge.

00:19:01.871 --> 00:19:03.890
un er iz gegangen tsu fus aheym.

00:19:05.415 --> 00:19:08.964
iz un-, nit dergeyendik shoyn di shtetl bay undz

00:19:09.009 --> 00:19:11.822
hot men im dortn, unter vegs, di hige poyerim

00:19:12.772 --> 00:19:13.914
derharget.

00:19:14.392 --> 00:19:16.609
un mayn foter iz geven zeyer a guter mentsh.

00:19:16.609 --> 00:19:17.916
zeyer gut geven

00:19:17.916 --> 00:19:21.069
far der, far di arbeter, far di hige mentshn

00:19:22.911 --> 00:19:23.937
un m'hot im

00:19:24.332 --> 00:19:26.048
derharget. iz geven a yid.

00:19:27.504 --> 00:19:32.527
ir hot epes getrofn BEKHOL ZOT epes kroyvim vos hobn ibergelebt demolstn?

00:19:32.735 --> 00:19:33.742
keynem nit.

00:19:33.478 --> 00:19:34.806
nokhn bafrayung?

00:19:34.170 --> 00:19:35.829
n- keynem nit. keyn...

00:19:34.980 --> 00:19:36.578
keyn shum kroyvim nisht?

00:19:35.829 --> 00:19:38.158
keyne kroy- ale zaynen umgekumen.

00:19:38.158 --> 00:19:39.344
ale kroyvim.

00:19:39.215 --> 00:19:41.403
di, ayer shvesterkind Rokhl?

00:19:40.312 --> 00:19:44.612
di shvesterkind, zi iz gekumen, mayn shvesterkind Rokhl hot zikh bafrayt

00:19:44.615 --> 00:19:47.540
bay, in Daytshland, bay di amerikaner

00:19:47.552 --> 00:19:51.023
un zi mitn man zaynen oykh geven in ITALIEN dakht zikh

00:19:51.399 --> 00:19:52.743
un etl- a f-

00:19:51.720 --> 00:19:54.617
ze- zey hobn zikh nisht, zey hobn nisht tsurikgeforn keyn Lite?

00:19:53.897 --> 00:19:55.615
Lite zaynen zey nit geforn.

00:19:55.615 --> 00:20:00.725
zaynen fun dortn shoyn, fun, gekumen do direkt in Yisroel in di fertsikster yorn.

00:20:00.917 --> 00:20:05.771
un d- ir hot zikh dervust vegn dem? ven hot ir zikh dervust vegn dem az s'hot ibergelebt di kuzine?

00:20:05.810 --> 00:20:10.895
o, shpet, shpet. mistome in di zekhtsikster, in di zibetsikster...

00:20:06.806 --> 00:20:07.864
shpet.

00:20:09.810 --> 00:20:11.812
a, biz demolst hot ir nisht gevust.

00:20:10.895 --> 00:20:14.056
keyn zakh nit gevust. dan keyn farbindung nit gehat.

00:20:17.623 --> 00:20:21.330
iz fun ayer shtetl hot ir zikh tsurikgekert keyn Kovne?

00:20:20.846 --> 00:20:23.020
ya, ikh bin geforn dos ⟨oyf⟩ nor a kuk ton

00:20:23.020 --> 00:20:25.459
un gekumen tsurik in Kovne.

00:20:25.459 --> 00:20:27.557
nu, m'hot dokh gemuzt lebn.

00:20:27.714 --> 00:20:28.299
zikh

00:20:28.828 --> 00:20:30.847
ayngeordnt oyf arbet

00:20:31.933 --> 00:20:34.917
s- ikh bin avek arbetn, me ⟨darft⟩ esn, me darf.

00:20:34.953 --> 00:20:38.199
nu, m'hot zikh bakant mit yugntlekhe. iz men dokh ⟨yungn⟩,

00:20:38.244 --> 00:20:41.495
zikh bakant mit mayn man, Elyezer Zilber.

00:20:42.446 --> 00:20:46.355
un er iz oykh gekumen fun geto, fun partizaner,

00:20:46.547 --> 00:20:50.383
eyner aleyn, keynem nit gefunen fun di gantse mishpokhe.

00:20:50.383 --> 00:20:53.966
alemen hot men oysgeharget in di lagern, in di getos.

00:20:55.406 --> 00:20:58.927
nu, mir hobn khasene gehat in finf un fertsikstn yor.

00:20:59.135 --> 00:21:00.665
tsentn AVGUST.

00:21:00.418 --> 00:21:03.652
kh'hob aykh gevolt fregn nokh a frage. zayendik bay aykh in shtetl

00:21:03.725 --> 00:21:07.550
ven ir zent gekumen zukhn, ⟨zen vos,⟩ zikh dervisn vos hot pasirt mit di mishpokhe

00:21:08.383 --> 00:21:13.119
 ayer hoyz, ayer, dos hot epes tsurikgeke- -krign?

00:21:12.028 --> 00:21:15.364
keyn zakh nit gefunen. alts opgebrent.

00:21:15.453 --> 00:21:17.805
az s'hot zikh ongefangen, kh'gey a bisl tsurik,

00:21:17.850 --> 00:21:19.898
az s'hot zikh ongefangen di milkhome

00:21:19.898 --> 00:21:21.169
zuntik

00:21:21.427 --> 00:21:23.278
iz donershtik

00:21:23.587 --> 00:21:26.264
hot men untergetsundn di kloyz

00:21:26.625 --> 00:21:28.526
un m'hot gezogt az di yidn

00:21:28.903 --> 00:21:30.467
hobn dos gemakht

00:21:30.708 --> 00:21:34.516
un dan hot men tsuzamengetribn glaykh ale yidn di ershte vokh.

00:21:35.062 --> 00:21:38.046
nu, m'hot zey gehaltn dortn a khoydesh a kurtse tsayt.

00:21:38.046 --> 00:21:39.613
m'hot alemen oysgeshosn.

00:21:39.770 --> 00:21:40.755
un dos hot men...

00:21:39.956 --> 00:21:41.418
keynem nit gefunen.

00:21:40.755 --> 00:21:42.651
in ale hayzer alts farbrent.

00:21:42.200 --> 00:21:44.607
f- alts farbrent, keyn zakh nit gefunen.

00:21:43.770 --> 00:21:46.701
dos hot ir zikh oykh dervust zayendik in shtetl.

00:21:44.900 --> 00:21:46.399
dervust az ikh bin gek-,

00:21:46.399 --> 00:21:48.196
ye, az ikh bin gekumen in shtetl

