ikh hob oykh gearbet in farshidene erter.

00:23:15.722 --> 00:23:18.332
nakher di letste tsvey un tsvantsik yor

00:23:18.540 --> 00:23:21.946
hobn mir shoyn tsuza- hobn mir gearbet, er hot shoyn oykh gearbet

00:23:21.946 --> 00:23:23.816
fun zeks un zibetsikstn yor

00:23:23.923 --> 00:23:26.452
in a proyektnem institut

00:23:26.452 --> 00:23:28.052
fun landvirtshaft

00:23:30.268 --> 00:23:32.406
bizn aroysforn in Yisroel.

00:23:32.985 --> 00:23:33.671
un

00:23:34.453 --> 00:23:35.471
in

00:23:35.499 --> 00:23:38.176
tsvey un zib- in dray un zibetsikstn yor

00:23:38.385 --> 00:23:38.922
g- m-

00:23:38.922 --> 00:23:40.573
mir hobn tsvey tekhter,

00:23:41.692 --> 00:23:44.684
beyde geendikt in Lite, in Kovne

00:23:44.684 --> 00:23:48.689
a insti- MEDITSINSKIY institut, beyde doktoyrim,

00:23:49.522 --> 00:23:53.161
