Lafer.

00:24:07.525 --> 00:24:08.872
loytn man, ye.

00:24:08.591 --> 00:24:10.037
un di tsveyte?

00:24:09.300 --> 00:24:12.146
di tsveyte heyst SONYA, oykh Zilber,

00:24:12.253 --> 00:24:13.429
Frishman.

00:24:13.502 --> 00:24:15.471
ven iz SONYA geboyrn gevorn?

00:24:15.172 --> 00:24:17.546
SONYA in nayntsn finf un fuftsik.

00:24:17.670 --> 00:24:19.453
hobn zey beyde zikh gelernt...

00:24:18.902 --> 00:24:21.194
gelernt, geendikt di mitlshuln

00:24:21.194 --> 00:24:22.493
in Kovne

00:24:22.493 --> 00:24:26.523
un nakher geendikt di institutn be- dem institut dem meditsinishn,

00:24:26.934 --> 00:24:30.635
un DORA iz avekgeforn mit ir mishpokhe, mit ir man,

00:24:30.635 --> 00:24:32.767
mit a meydele ILANA,

00:24:32.958 --> 00:24:36.327
in dray, in tsvey un zi- in tsvey un zibetsikstn yor.

00:24:36.047 --> 00:24:39.366
me- m'hot zey laykht aroysgelozt? zey hobn nisht gegat keyn shverikeytn?

00:24:38.898 --> 00:24:43.089
neyn, m'hot aroysgelozn. dem, ir man's eltern zaynen shoyn geven

00:24:43.089 --> 00:24:46.250
frier avekgeforn in eyn un zibetsikstn yor.

00:24:46.357 --> 00:24:51.577
nakher hobn zey ongegebn, un mir hobn gemuzt gebn a erloybenish untershraybn

00:24:51.577 --> 00:24:53.526
az mir zaynen maskem,

00:24:53.526 --> 00:24:54.918
zikh untergeshribn.

00:24:54.918 --> 00:24:57.101
hot ⟨dort⟩ gearbet in arkhiv mayn man,

00:24:57.292 --> 00:25:00.155
m'hot zikh untergeshribn, un m'hot zey aroysgelozn.

00:25:00.752 --> 00:25:03.424
ober unterdesn, az zi iz geven in Yisroel

00:25:03.424 --> 00:25:05.842
sh- az zi hot shoyn gelebt hob ikh gevelt forn

00:25:06.118 --> 00:25:07.296
tsu bazukh,

00:25:07.333 --> 00:25:10.055
gekrogn zeks mol ENTSAGUNGEN.

00:25:10.083 --> 00:25:13.672
m'hot mir nit aroysgelozn tsu bazukh vayle er hot gearbet

00:25:14.403 --> 00:25:16.220
in arkhiv, mayn man.

00:25:16.648 --> 00:25:17.312
nu,

00:25:17.357 --> 00:25:21.049
nit aroysgelozn. iz ober in nayntsn akht un akhtsik

00:25:21.049 --> 00:25:22.869
iz mayn man geforn tsu bazukh

00:25:23.111 --> 00:25:23.733
do.

00:25:23.733 --> 00:25:26.008
dan iz shoyn, zikh alts gebitn dan,

00:25:26.402 --> 00:25:28.472
a bisl bay undz, der gantser

00:25:28.967 --> 00:25:30.413
stroy, vi me zogt.

00:25:31.059 --> 00:25:34.209
iz er geven do tsvey monat tsu bazukh.

00:25:35.160 --> 00:25:35.948
nu,

00:25:36.392 --> 00:25:39.441
gekumen a tsufridener, zeyer gefelik geven,

00:25:39.750 --> 00:25:40.537
gekumen

00:25:40.830 --> 00:25:41.888
bashlosn

00:25:42.483 --> 00:25:43.524
me darf forn.

00:25:44.019 --> 00:25:47.422
iz di klenere tokhter iz geblibn mit aykh in Kovne,

00:25:45.926 --> 00:25:48.180
ya, mit undz in Kovne un...

00:25:47.546 --> 00:25:55.339
yetst hob ikh aykh gevolt fregn a frage a bisele nokh tsurik. lebndik fun finef un fertsikstn bizn nayntsikstn, in finef un fertsikstn yor

00:25:55.342 --> 00:25:59.403
dort in Lite, di greste tsayt unter di sovyetishe makht

00:25:58.953 --> 00:26:00.500
ye, di gantse tsayt.

00:26:00.236 --> 00:26:01.701
als yidn...

00:26:01.701 --> 00:26:05.259
ir hot oyfgetsoygn tsvey kinder, zey hobn zikh gelernt, shtudirt.

00:26:06.311 --> 00:26:09.565
hot zikh gefilt epes antisemitishkeyt in di ale yorn,

00:26:09.602 --> 00:26:12.988
hot ir gehat epes faln vos ir hot gefilt als yidn az...?

00:26:12.993 --> 00:26:21.256
nu, s'iz geven f- efsher farshidene azane faln, ober in algemeyn az di kinder hobn gelernt hobn zey zikh nit geshpirt, neyn, neyn, neyn, neyn.

00:26:19.136 --> 00:26:20.835
mm neyn. m'hot zey nisht getshepet.

00:26:21.785 --> 00:26:26.167
nu, ober azoy hot zikh epes a andert mol hot zikh ye vos geshpirt, ober

00:26:26.913 --> 00:26:27.900
nit azoy.

00:26:27.337 --> 00:26:31.854
s'iz geven dortn yidn vos ir flegt zikh trefn tsvishn zikh?

00:26:31.438 --> 00:26:33.671
ye, ⟨a min,⟩ dan, yene yorn

00:26:33.671 --> 00:26:37.794
iz geven a sakh nokh yidn bizn ⟨iber⟩ bizn tsvey un zibetsikstn yor.

00:26:38.087 --> 00:26:41.704
in tsvey un zibetsik yor iz geven a groyse ALIYA fun undz fun Lite.

00:26:41.715 --> 00:26:44.978
nor geven a sakh yidn, khaveyrim, ale partizaner

00:26:44.978 --> 00:26:48.142
vos zaynen gekumen tsuzamen fun vald mit mayn man.

00:26:46.794 --> 00:26:48.105
flegn zikh trefn.

00:26:48.142 --> 00:26:51.044
yo, mir flegn zikh trefn, un me flegt opmerkn ale

00:26:51.044 --> 00:26:53.347
yontoyvim yidishe, un

00:26:53.347 --> 00:26:55.229
farshteyt zikh un sovyetishe,

00:26:55.265 --> 00:26:57.676
un z- me flegt reydn nor yidish.

00:26:57.676 --> 00:26:59.580
nu, mir hobn geredt nor yidish.

00:26:59.568 --> 00:27:01.419
m'hot aykh nisht getshepet vegn dem.

00:27:00.243 --> 00:27:03.312
keyner nit. in gas flegt men geyn un reydn yidish.

00:27:03.312 --> 00:27:07.342
dos hobn shoyn di litviner f- gevust az yidn reydn yidish bay undz.

00:27:09.255 --> 00:27:11.241
yetst

00:27:11.887 --> 00:27:14.399
di tokhter iz avekgeforn keyn Yisroel

00:27:13.970 --> 00:27:14.505
ye.

00:27:14.399 --> 00:27:22.176
hot men aykh oykh ⟨dokh⟩ nisht getshepet di, di ale yorn? m'hot aykh gelozt, ir hot gehat korespondents mit der tokhter, ir hot zikh gekent tsuzamenshraybn, ir hot gevust...

00:27:21.371 --> 00:27:26.372
az zi iz avekgeforn hot nokh mayn man dray yor g- hot men nokh im gelozn arbetn dray yor i-

00:27:26.372 --> 00:27:27.862
in tsen- in arkhiv

00:27:28.104 --> 00:27:29.482
vi a direktor nokh.

