nakher iz ariber shoyn dray yor, hot men shoyn gegebn a bisl

00:27:34.297 --> 00:27:35.070
on-

00:27:35.090 --> 00:27:37.160
-tsuhern az s'iz shoyn genug.

00:27:37.352 --> 00:27:38.410
me darf a-

00:27:38.550 --> 00:27:39.608
baytn.

00:27:40.355 --> 00:27:45.007
nu, iz, iz er avek shoyn dan fun arkhiv un ariber arbetn in dem proyektnem

00:27:45.553 --> 00:27:47.825
institut far landvirtshaft.

00:27:48.489 --> 00:27:50.795
dortn hot er oykh opgearbet zekhtsn yor.

00:27:53.957 --> 00:27:58.392
nu, mit di tokhter hobn mir gefirt a korespondents di gantse tsayt. ya, ya.

00:27:56.977 --> 00:27:57.697
yo?

00:27:58.395 --> 00:27:59.101
ya.

